query:
SELECT "t"."name", COUNT("pt"."photo_id") as "count!"
        FROM "tag" "t"
        JOIN "photo_tag" "pt" ON "t"."id" = "pt"."tag_id"
        JOIN "photo" "p" ON "pt"."photo_id" = "p"."id"
        WHERE "p"."user_id" = $1
        GROUP BY "t"."name"
        HAVING COUNT("pt"."photo_id") > 0
        ORDER BY "count!" DESC
